l reveal-up"> <p class="text-terra text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-2">FAQ</p> <h2 class="text-xl md:text-3xl font-black text-text">よくあるご質問</h2> </div> <div class="space-y-3 stagger-children"> <div x-data="{ open: false }" class="reveal reveal-up bg-bg rounded-2xl border border-border shadow-sm overflow-hidden card-hover"> <button x-on:click="open = !open" class="w-full flex items-start justify-between gap-4 p-5 md:p-6 text-left cursor-pointer" x-bind:aria-expanded="open.toString()"> <div class="flex items-start gap-3"> <span class="bg-gradient-to-br from-terra to-amber text-white w-7 h-7 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 shadow">Q</span> <span class="text-text font-bold text-sm leading-relaxed">出張費や見積もり費用はかかりますか？</span> </div> <span class="text-terra text-xl flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200" x-bind:class="open && 'rotate-45'">+</span> </button> <div x-show="open" x-transition:enter="transition ease-out duration-200" x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0 -translate-y-2" x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100 translate-y-0" class="px-5 md:px-6 pb-5 md:pb-6" style="display: none;"> <div class="flex items-start gap-3 pl-0 md:pl-10"> <span class="bg-dark text-white w-7 h-7 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold flex-shrink-0 shadow">A</span> <p class="text-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed">いいえ。出張費・見積もり・査定費はすべて無料です。査定だけのご相談でも費用はかかりません。</p> </div> </div> </div><div x-data="{ open: false }" class="reveal reveal-up bg-bg rounded-2xl border border-border shadow-sm overflow-hidden card-hover"> <button x-on:click="open = !open" class="w-full flex items-start justify-between gap-4 p-5 md:p-6 text-left cursor-pointer" x-bind:aria-expanded="open.toString()"> <div class="flex items-start gap-3"> <span class="bg-gradient-to-br from-terra to-amber text-white w-7 h-7 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 shadow">Q</span> <span class="text-text font-bold text-sm leading-relaxed">名古屋でどんな出張買取・不用品回収を相談できますか？</span> </div> <span class="text-terra text-xl flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200" x-bind:class="open && 'rotate-45'">+</span> </button> <div x-show="open" x-transition:enter="transition ease-out duration-200" x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0 -translate-y-2" x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100 translate-y-0" class="px-5 md:px-6 pb-5 md:pb-6" style="display: none;"> <div class="flex items-start gap-3 pl-0 md:pl-10"> <span class="bg-dark text-white w-7 h-7 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold flex-shrink-0 shadow">A</span> <p class="text-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed">冷蔵庫・洗濯機・エアコン・テレビなどの不用品買取、家具、ブランド品、貴金属の出張買取に加えて、不用品回収、引越し前の片付け、遺品整理、家じまい、残置物撤去までまとめてご相談いただけます。</p> </div> </div> </div><div x-data="{ open: false }" class="reveal reveal-up bg-bg rounded-2xl border border-border shadow-sm overflow-hidden card-hover"> <button x-on:click="open = !open" class="w-full flex items-start justify-between gap-4 p-5 md:p-6 text-left cursor-pointer" x-bind:aria-expanded="open.toString()"> <div class="flex items-start gap-3"> <span class="bg-gradient-to-br from-terra to-amber text-white w-7 h-7 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 shadow">Q</span> <span class="text-text font-bold text-sm leading-relaxed">名古屋なら最短どのくらいで来てもらえますか？</span> </div> <span class="text-terra text-xl flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200" x-bind:class="open && 'rotate-45'">+</span> </button> <div x-show="open" x-transition:enter="transition ease-out duration-200" x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0 -translate-y-2" x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100 translate-y-0" class="px-5 md:px-6 pb-5 md:pb-6" style="display: none;"> <div class="flex items-start gap-3 pl-0 md:pl-10"> <span class="bg-dark text-white w-7 h-7 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold flex-shrink-0 shadow">A</span> <p class="text-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed">最短30分でご相談可能です。ご予約状況とエリアによっては即日訪問にも対応しています。</p> </div> </div> </div><div x-data="{ open: false }" class="reveal reveal-up bg-bg rounded-2xl border border-border shadow-sm overflow-hidden card-hover"> <button x-on:click="open = !open" class="w-full flex items-start justify-between gap-4 p-5 md:p-6 text-left cursor-pointer" x-bind:aria-expanded="open.toString()"> <div class="flex items-start gap-3"> <span class="bg-gradient-to-br from-terra to-amber text-white w-7 h-7 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 shadow">Q</span> <span class="text-text font-bold text-sm leading-relaxed">LINEで写真を送って出張買取の相談はできますか？</span> </div> <span class="text-terra text-xl flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200" x-bind:class="open && 'rotate-45'">+</span> </button> <div x-show="open" x-transition:enter="transition ease-out duration-200" x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0 -translate-y-2" x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100 translate-y-0" class="px-5 md:px-6 pb-5 md:pb-6" style="display: none;"> <div class="flex items-start gap-3 pl-0 md:pl-10"> <span class="bg-dark text-white w-7 h-7 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold flex-shrink-0 shadow">A</span> <p class="text-text-light text-sm leading-relaxed">はい。LINEで写真を送っていただければ、概算のご案内や当日の流れを先にお伝えできます。電話が難しい場合にも便利です。</p> </div> </div> </div><div x-data="{ open: false }" class="reveal reveal-up bg-bg rounded-2xl border border-border shadow-sm overflow-hidden card-hover"> <button x-on:click="open = !open" class="w-full flex items-start justify-between gap-4 p-5 md:p-6 text-left cursor-pointer" x-bind:aria-expanded="open.toString()"> <div class="flex items-start gap-3"> <span class="bg-gradient-to-br from-terra to-amber text-white w-7 h-7 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5 shadow">Q</span> <span class="text-text font-bold text-sm leading-relaxed">支払い方法はどうなりますか？</span> </div> <span class="text-terra text-xl flex-shrink-0 transit